{"tid":206808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片)【蟹貨之王】天巒慘蝕705萬 「鬼城」蝕讓比例達八成","createTime":"2017-04-18T14:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T17:43:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a894919c12dc18d659bd5f213dc6bf7fcaf99d6e","tid":206808,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170418/large/1492517302_af43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170418%2Flarge%2F1492517302_af43.jpg&h=31b9711c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有「鬼城」之稱的上水洋房天巒再錄蝕讓。<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，天巒1期因特拉肯大道單號屋，實用面積2,048方呎，成交價3,300萬元，呎價16,113元。原業主2010年10月向新地（016）以3,809.8萬元買入單位，賬面已蝕509.8萬元，若計及釐印費及佣金等開支，料損手約705萬元。<br />\n天巒屬全港蟹貨重災區之一，劈價血流成河。中原地產註冊成交顯示，近兩年來天巒錄18宗買賣成交，多達15宗屬蝕讓，比例83%。大埔比華利山別墅亦是本港著名蟹貨重災區，近兩年錄37宗成交，蝕讓佔24宗或65%。因此，若以比例計，天巒絕對可稱為「蟹貨之王」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170418/56580007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170418%2F56580007&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=7cf97bc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170418%2F56580007&h=96d2630b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170418/56580007</a>"},{"pid":"f32fdc3ea34c166095c937d09565452f96796e31","tid":206808,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2df2e1cf9fa7b9b9f21051f39c25e85ca25f8e","tid":206808,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"上水買不如番大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66395a0f94dabcfb3c32d79bf443d728e1a6679d","tid":206808,"uid":41317,"like":0,"di